    "endTime": 4.129,
    "text": "I don't know, what do you wanna do today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.213,
    "endTime": 6.59,
    "text": "I don't know, what do you wanna do today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.8,
    "endTime": 11.303,
    "text": "I know what I want to do today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.359,
    "endTime": 28.237000000000002,
    "text": "This show was filmed in front of a live studio audience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.197,
    "endTime": 32.198,
    "text": "I need some money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.202,
    "endTime": 36.202,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.663,
    "endTime": 39.33,
    "text": "Maybe we can borrow money from Squidward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.414,
    "endTime": 42.668,
    "text": "Wait, instead of borrowing the money,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.126,
    "endTime": 46.213,
    "text": "why don't we just borrow the balloon?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.296,
    "endTime": 48.298,
    "text": "It's just borrowing, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.382,
    "endTime": 52.01,
    "text": "Yeah, and borrowing is OK as long as we bring it back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.094,
    "endTime": 52.5,
    "text": "Right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.5,
    "endTime": 53.303,
    "text": "Right!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.18,
    "endTime": 57.099,
    "text": "This is so great!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.182,
    "endTime": 58.934000000000005,
    "text": "We're gonna have so much fun!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.017,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "We love borrowing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.15,
    "endTime": 69.403,
    "text": "How are we gonna return it now, SpongeBob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.486,
    "endTime": 71.363,
    "text": "I've got the pieces!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "I've got the air!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.446,
    "endTime": 72.698,
    "text": "Hurry, put the pieces on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.742,
    "endTime": 76.74300000000001,
    "text": "You popped the balloon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.327,
    "endTime": 78.37,
    "text": "We can't return it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.246,
    "endTime": 80.163,
    "text": "We're thieves!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.915,
    "endTime": 84.126,
    "text": "It's not safe in Bikini Bottom anymore!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.334,
    "endTime": 86.545,
    "text": "We've gotta move fast and cover our tracks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.421,
    "endTime": 88.79700000000001,
    "text": "I'm on it SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.095,
    "endTime": 96.096,
    "text": "I guess..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.43,
    "endTime": 99.766,
    "text": "I'll pack up my stuff and get ready to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.392,
    "endTime": 101.393,
    "text": "My..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.768,
    "endTime": 102.769,
    "text": "Clothes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.854,
    "endTime": 105.189,
    "text": "Patrick, those are my clothes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.272,
    "endTime": 107.191,
    "text": "My peanut butter!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.441,
    "endTime": 108.73400000000001,
    "text": "That's my peanut butter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.901,
    "endTime": 109.86,
    "text": "And my pickles!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.404,
    "endTime": 114.155,
    "text": "I can't believe you're leaving, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.239,
    "endTime": 115.908,
    "text": "With all my pickles!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.825,
    "endTime": 119.328,
    "text": "Patrick Star will live no more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.62,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "Forever!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.039,
    "text": "In Bikini Bottom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.999,
    "endTime": 126.877,
    "text": "But, what if you weren't Patrick Star?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.96,
    "endTime": 127.961,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.548,
    "endTime": 132.549,
    "text": "He--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.968,
    "endTime": 139.05499999999998,
    "text": "And who are you, my rubenesque beauty?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.139,
    "endTime": 141.05800000000002,
    "text": "That's Patricia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.141,
    "endTime": 143.101,
    "text": "Our newest Krusty Krab employee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.31,
    "endTime": 146.063,
    "text": "Well, she sure is stunning!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.072,
    "endTime": 155.989,
    "text": "Eh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.073,
    "endTime": 161.328,
    "text": "You know, Patricia, they don't call me \"The Sizzle-lips Squid\" for nothing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.622,
    "endTime": 165.62400000000002,
    "text": "So, are you free this Saturday night?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.832,
    "endTime": 166.834,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.042,
    "endTime": 169.37800000000001,
    "text": "- That's the night SpongeBob and I-- - SpongeBob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.586,
    "endTime": 171.88000000000002,
    "text": "Get back to work, you go beggin' freeloader!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.964,
    "endTime": 174.466,
    "text": "Hut to, hut to! Ya! Ya!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.55,
    "endTime": 175.92600000000002,
    "text": "Well, now that we're alone,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.009,
    "endTime": 178.595,
    "text": "How would you like to by my date Friday night to a--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.679,
    "endTime": 179.721,
    "text": "Well, I can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.805,
    "endTime": 183.1,
    "text": "SpongeBob and I will be flying submarines that night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.684,
    "endTime": 186.645,
    "text": "I have to get back to krusting the krab."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.145,
    "endTime": 188.18800000000002,
    "text": "Man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.272,
    "endTime": 190.19,
    "text": "Why are those two so nice to me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.44,
    "endTime": 192.401,
    "text": "They were never this nice to Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.818,
    "endTime": 193.90200000000002,
    "text": "It's weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.653,
    "endTime": 196.363,
    "text": "Are you sure about Saturday night?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.323,
    "endTime": 199.70000000000002,
    "text": "Persistent much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.492,
    "endTime": 201.702,
    "text": "How about Sunday brunch?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.785,
    "endTime": 203.704,
    "text": "No thanks again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.248,
    "endTime": 207.89999999999998,
    "text": "But I made reservations for two at--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.9,
    "endTime": 209.084,
    "text": "I said no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.253,
    "endTime": 212.254,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.921,
    "endTime": 213.839,
    "text": "No way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.922,
    "endTime": 215.465,
    "text": "No. No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.674,
    "endTime": 216.675,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.301,
    "endTime": 220.387,
    "text": "What is it about me that makes those two so friendly?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.554,
    "endTime": 223.18200000000002,
    "text": "Must have something to do with this disguise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.057,
    "endTime": 225.893,
    "text": "I can't wear this any longer!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.143,
    "endTime": 229.938,
    "text": "But if you reveal your secret identity, you'll have to leave Bikini Bottom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.022,
    "endTime": 233.691,
    "text": "Well I'm sorry, SpongeBob. I just can't live like this anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.775,
    "endTime": 236.695,
    "text": "I'm tired of pretending to be someone I'm not!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 242.826,
    "text": "I have an announcement to make."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.997,
    "endTime": 248.12300000000002,
    "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.498,
    "endTime": 251.584,
    "text": "So, let me get this straight. You're not a woman?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.752,
    "endTime": 252.75300000000001,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.091,
    "endTime": 259.259,
    "text": "You have a visitor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.597,
    "endTime": 265.64,
    "text": "- Who is it? - Hello, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.768,
    "endTime": 270.395,
    "text": "What happened to prisoner 665321?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.817,
    "endTime": 278.445,
    "text": "Let's go home, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.612,
    "endTime": 279.90500000000003,
    "text": "But, who are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.495,
    "endTime": 287.955,
    "text": "No, seriously. Who are you?"
  }
]